Summary: Captured 2 sonic booms of UFOs but there was no boom
divs: Sighting DetailsSo i was doing exposure photos with my Canon t3i of this really cool road, so i was trying different angles and captured some sort of yellow and greenish sonic booms i guess you can say. i mean that's the closest thing i can say to describe it. It was unable to be seen by the naked eye when this event was taking place. i noticed these booms when i was reviewing the photo in my car when i packed up... i didn't notice it till afterwards.
